Subject: ANDROID: rust: miscdevice: add llseek

Support for this method was sent upstream before [1] but was not accepted
as no upstream driver uses llseek().

[1] https://lore.kernel.org/all/20251015040246.151141-1-ryasuoka@redhat.com/

